South Africa to Publish Revised Carbon Tax Proposals This Year

-- B y   M i k e   C o h e n
-- 
2011-10-03T07:41:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/south-africa-to-publish-revised-carbon-tax-proposals-this-year.html
South Africa  plans to publish revised
proposals on carbon taxes later this year, Finance Minister
 Pravin Gordhan  said.  The government received 70 written submissions after
publishing a discussion document on carbon taxes and is
discussing the issue with the  mining industry , Gordhan said in a
written reply to a parliamentary question e-mailed from  Cape
Town  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mike Cohen in Cape Town at 
 mcohen21@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
